8.假设程序的开头有下列声明：
int imate = 2;
long shot = 53456;
char grade = 'A';
float log = 2.71828;

把下面printf() 语句中的转换字符补充完整：

printf("The odds against the %d were %ld to 1.\n", imate, shot);
printf("A score of %c is not an %f grade.\n", log, grade);

9.假设ch是char类型的变量，分别使用转义序列，十进制、八进制字符常量和十六进制字符常量把回车字符赋给ch（假设使用ASCII编码值）。
printf("Hello, World!  %c \n",'\r');
printf("Hello, World! %c \n",13);
printf("Hello, World! %c \n",0x0d);
printf("Hello, World! %c \n",015);




10.修正下面的程序（在C中，/表示除以）。
void main(int)/ this program is perfact /
{
	cows, legs integer;
	printf("How many cow legs did you count?\n);
	scanf("%c", legs);
	cows = legs / 4;
	printf("That implies threr are %f cows.\n", cows)
}

  a.缺少#include 
  b.main 参数应该为 void
  c.cows, legs, integer; 应该为：float cows, legs, integer;
  d.scanf("%c", legs); 应该为 scanf("%f", legs);
  e.缺少return 0;
11.指出下列转义序列的含义
a.\n
b.\\
c.\"
d.\t

  1.换行
  2.\
  3."
  d.制表符


